<%= render 'header' %>
<div class="container new-home">
  <div class="row">
    <aside class="complementary" role="complementary">
      <section class="mod action">
        <h2 class="giga">What I'm Up To...</h2>
        <%= render 'facebook_widget' %>
      </section>
    </aside>


      <div class='iosslider main' role="main">
        <div class = 'slider'>
          <div class='slide'>
            <img src="assets/home_5.jpg"/>
          </div>
          <div class='slide'>
            <img src="assets/home_3.jpg"/>
          </div>
          <div class='slide'>
            <img src="assets/home_1.jpg"/>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </section>


  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="moto">Meeting challenges, working together!</div>
    <p id='endorse'>Endorsements:</p>
    <div class='iosslider endorse'>
      <div class='slider'>
        <div class='slide'>
          Maine AFL-CIO
        </div>
        <div class='slide'>
          Maine Education Association
        </div>
        <div class='slide'>
          MSEA-SEIU
        </div>
        <div class='slide'>
          Sierra Club Maine
        </div>
        <div class='slide'>
          Maine People's Alliance
        </div>
        <div class='slide'>
          Planned Parenthood Maine
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <section class="main" style="width:530px">
    <header class="heading">
      <p>From My Desk...</p>
    </header>
    <div class="hfeed">
      <article class="hentry">
        <header>
          <h2 class="entry-title giga"></h2>
        </header>
        <script src="http://daveformaine.tumblr.com/js" type="text/javascript"></script>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <aside class="complementary" role="complementary" style="width:450px;border-left: 2px solid #0194c9;margin-right: -2px;">
    <div class="heading">
      Together, we can...
    </div>
    <div class="letter">
      <p>
        Friends and Neighbors,
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for the opportunity to be a voice for the interests of ​Knox County ​Senate District 12. I believe government is local and your voice makes a difference. To represent you, I need to hear ​from ​you, so please don't hesitate to contact​ me​. I am here to serve you​!​
      </p>
      <p>
        This was a busy session, but there's much more to be done in the coming ​year includ​ing alternative energy generation, taking care of our ​elderly and children, supporting small Maine businesses and helping our education systems evolve to meet the needs of our students.
      </p>
      <p>We have the resources, the ideas and the people to meet any challenge we face together.</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for allowing me to help build a stronger Maine​ for us all​​.
      </p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>
<%= render 'footer' %>